<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1937-12-18T23:00:00-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1937-12-18T23:00:00-05:00" n="660" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d660">
                        <note rend="inline" type="source">394.115 Panay/151: Telegram</note>
                        <head><hi rend="italic">The Ambassador in Japan</hi> (<persName type="from"><hi rend="italic">Grew</hi></persName>) <hi rend="italic">to
                                the <gloss type="to">Secretary of State</gloss></hi></head>
                        <opener>
                            <dateline rendition="#right"><placeName><hi rend="smallcaps">Tokyo</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1937-12-19T13:00:00+09:00">December 19, 1937—1
                                p.m.</date><lb/>[Received December 19—2:22 a.m.]</dateline>
                        </opener>
                        <p>657. We asked Yoshizawa this morning when replies to our signed note of
                            December 14<note n="89" xml:id="d660fn89">See telegram No. 631, December
                                14, 9 p.m., <ref target="frus1931-41v01#pg_526"><hi rend="italic">Foreign Relations</hi>, Japan, 1931–1941, vol. <hi rend="smallcaps">i</hi>, p. 526</ref>.</note> and <hi rend="italic">aide-mémoire</hi> of December 17<note n="90" xml:id="d660fn90">See telegram No. 647, December 17, 1 p.m., <ref target="frus1931-41v01#pg_528"><hi rend="italic">ibid</hi>., p.
                                    528</ref>.</note> would be <pb facs="0520" n="512" xml:id="pg_512"/> made. He replied that the charge of Japanese
                            machine-gunning of the <hi rend="italic">Panay</hi> having been made,
                            the Japanese Government must first ascertain the facts. He confirmed
                            that an officer of the General Staff had left for Shanghai to
                            investigate.</p>
                        <closer><signed><hi rend="smallcaps">Grew</hi></signed></closer>
                    </div>
                    </body></text></TEI>